{"tid":1617561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美參議員收到林鄭信件，批評內容空泛","createTime":"2019-10-04T00:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:59:17.000Z","uid":6103,"like":1128,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"99fee9abcc72f2d87fae408dc1bd639b8e79639a","tid":1617561,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:00:28.000Z","msg":"美國參議員斯科特稱收到行政長官林鄭月娥寄給他的信，批評內容空泛。<br />\n<br />\n斯科特數天前曾訪港，並親身觀察示威情況。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他透露曾與林鄭月娥會面，指對方當時無法回答對於有關港人基本人權的疑問，並在當地周四再收到林鄭月娥的信件回覆</span></span>。批評內容是更多空話，其無所作為，顯示她不重視香港人權，包括拒絕市民和平集會的權利。<br />\n<br />\n直言林鄭月娥只是國家主席習近平稱霸世界的棋子，又指<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國將致力幫助港人抗爭，不會退縮。</span></span>林鄭月娥則於信中表示期望斯科特理解美國改變對港政策或作相關立法將帶來的負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/558502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F558502&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=1ad091e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F558502&h=70523c43\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/558502</a>"},{"pid":"ab85fbafb08f28e1bbedf00aac5825bab43c3dd1","tid":1617561,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:04:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e6903ba8b1660c218b2041f49d95f907428b0527","tid":1617561,"uid":229436,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:06:47.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21cd7a133a1b11f8ec630c2aa4cd0cd7ca7f627","tid":1617561,"uid":8948,"like":116,"dislike":2,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:08:45.000Z","msg":"墨寫的謊言<br />\n掩蓋不了<br />\n血寫的真相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /